N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 5327.3 - Placement on the excluded persons list

State Regulations

The placement of a person on the excluded persons list
shall have the effect of requiring the exclusion or ejection of the excluded
person from all New York State licensed gaming facilities. Notes
